title: RD Wingfield - The Killing Season - 1984 - BBC Audio Drama
description:
The Killing Season - BBC 1984 - R.D.Wingfield (as A.Jefferson) - Audio Drama
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

It's Christmas Eve at Melford Police Station, the season of 'goodwill' to all men. However, a fire supposedly started by vandals leads swiftly and surprisingly to murder and an end to any kind of goodwill.

Six part thriller with Michael Jenner, Sean Barrett, John Hollis, Manning Wilson and Allan Cuthbertson. First broadcast in Jan 1984.

(6x30 mins)
